## How did I discover the vulnerability?

- First go to expedia site and then login to your account.

yes i am logged in and the vulnerability is located exactly in the steps of logging in and logging out.
but i found it while logging out first and i will explain how to logout.

- As you can see, the "rurl" parameter in the lower left part catches our eye. So what exactly does this do?

The "rurl" parameter redirects you to the homepage when you log out, but I already said I found a way to redirect it to another site.
